(345, 1, '2014-07-07 09:20:32', '2014-07-07 09:20:32', 'Finally.\r\n\r\nThat’s actually the first word that came out of my mouth when I saw Kana''s website go live. After months and months of talking about it, we finally got off our asses and did it!\r\n\r\nIt gives me mixed feelings between the relief that it’s finally finished, the happiness that it’s finally finished and the pride that it’s finally finished... * lol * yups, all feelings revolve around the pleasant fact that it IS finally finished.\r\n\r\nThe Kana Website project is actually the one that I think is most important and remarkable, because in the digital world, a company''s website is sure to be the gateway to the public''s first impression.\r\n\r\nThis website pretty much depicts what Kana really is, a company that consists of a group of people whom I consider as my second family, a group of people who are all fun, witty, smart, dedicated and keep giving me reasons to truly love the work I do and to love each one of them for what they are with all their strengths and even greater excellencies.\r\n\r\nI personally see no flaws in ParaKana, because I do believe that every flaw can always be overcomed through learning process; such process that will perfect any imperfection and eventually turn it into an advantage.\r\n\r\nTo put it simply, I love them. (and love as we know it, is blind, so yeah maybe that’s why I only see the good in them).\r\n\r\nWithout them all, Kana would not be what it is today.\r\n\r\nI dedicate this first post to ParaKana, those who are still part of Kana, Kana’s clients, friends of Kana and not least those who were once part of Kana’s big family. I still think of them as family;\r\njust as they say, "Out of sight, near by heart..."\r\n\r\n<em>(ed: “ParaKana” is the term we use to represent ALL Kana family members whenever we need to tag everyone in a social media post)</em>\r\n\r\nSo welcome, have a seat and come witness our –still long– journey. A journey that will always be full of fun. Enjoy!\r\n\r\nTo be continued...\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n~ Vera\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'An Exciting Milestone in Our Journey', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'an-exciting-milestone-in-our-journey', '', '', '2014-07-11 08:00:52', '2014-07-11 08:00:52', '', 0, 'http://preview.kanadigital.com/kana-website/?p=345', 0, 'post', '', 0),
