a campaign really went - in plain numbers. You can go the extra mile by adding <em>sentiment</em> to this to understand which way it went, viral negative or viral positive.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Viral reach is only one of the countless metrics that can be derived from enriched social data. I’ll be covering more important metrics and milestones in upcoming posts.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Social Data Metrics That Reflect ROI (1)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-07 13:17:30', '2014-07-07 13:17:30', '', 1, 'http://preview.kanadigital.com/kana-website/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
